import { Box, Stack, Text, Button, Center  } from '@chakra-ui/react'

function App() {
  return (
    <Box justifyItems='center'>
      <Stack spacing={0} direction='column'>
        <Stack spacing={0} direction='row'>
          <Center  w="100%" alignContent='center' backgroundColor='#81ecec'>
            <Button colorScheme="#81ecec" variant="ghost" color="white" size='lg' fontSize='x-large' onClick={()=> console.log(this.value)}> {Button.colorScheme} </Button>
          </Center >
          <Box w="100%">
            <Text fontWeight='bold' fontSize='large' backgroundColor='#74b9ff' color='white' p='15vh' textAlign='center'> #74b9ff </Text>
          </Box>
          <Box w="100%">
            <Text fontWeight='bold' fontSize='large' backgroundColor='#a29bfe' color='white' p='15vh' textAlign='center'> #a29bfe </Text>
          </Box>
        </Stack>
        <Stack spacing={0} direction='row'>
        <Box w="100%">
          <Text fontWeight='bold' fontSize='large' backgroundColor='#00cec9' color='white' p='15vh' textAlign='center'> #00cec9 </Text>
        </Box>
        <Box w="100%">
         <Text fontWeight='bold' fontSize='large' backgroundColor='#0984e3' color='white' p='15vh' textAlign='center'> #0984e3 </Text>
        </Box>
        <Box w="100%">
          <Text fontWeight='bold' fontSize='large' backgroundColor='#6c5ce7' color='white' p='15vh' textAlign='center'> #6c5ce7 </Text>
        </Box>
        </Stack>
        <Stack spacing={0} direction='row'>
        <Box w="100%">
          <Text fontWeight='bold' fontSize='large' backgroundColor='#fab1a0' color='white' p='15vh' textAlign='center'>#fab1a0 </Text>
        </Box>
        <Box w="100%">
          <Text fontWeight='bold' fontSize='large' backgroundColor='#ff7675' color='white' p='15vh' textAlign='center'> #ff7675</Text>
        </Box>
        <Box w="100%">
          <Text fontWeight='bold' fontSize='large' backgroundColor='#fd79a8' color='white' p='15vh' textAlign='center'> #fd79a8 </Text>
        </Box>
        </Stack>
      </Stack>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default App;
